detaileddescription.para:
The result value returned by ADC_convert() is a raw value. The following uses ADC_convertToMicroVolts() to convert the raw value into microvolts. int_fast16_tres;
uint_fast16_tadcValue;
uint32_tadcValueUv;

res=ADC_convert(adc,&adcValue);
if(res==ADC_STATUS_SUCCESS)
{
adcValueUv=ADC_convertToMicroVolts(adc,adcValue);
}
